e=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;有权取消代理红利，并取消代理账号。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:28px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;3.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;代理旗下的会员不得开设多于一个的帐户。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;平台&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;有权要求会员提供有效的身份证明以验证会员的身份，并保留以&lt;/span&gt;IP&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;判定是否重复会员的权利。如违反上述事项，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;平台&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;有权终止玩家进行&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;购彩&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;并封存帐号及所有于&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;购彩&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;中赚取的&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;彩&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;金。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:28px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;4.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;代理不可为自己或其他下的有效投注会员&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;只能是公司直属下的有效投注会员&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;代理每月需有&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;个下线有效投注（有效投注为每周至少上线&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;次进行正常投注），如有违反协议&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;平台&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;有权终止并封存帐号及所有在&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;购彩&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;中赚取的&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;佣&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;金。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:28px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;5.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;如代理旗下的会员因为违反条例而被禁止享用&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;平台&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;的&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;购彩&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;，或&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;平台&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;退回存款给会员，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;平台&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;将不会分配相应的佣金给代理。如代理旗下会员存款用的信用卡、银行资料须经审核，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;平台&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;保留相关佣金直至审核完成。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:28px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;6.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;合约内的条件会以&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;平台&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;通知接受代理加入后开始执行。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;平台&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;及代理可随时终止此合约，在任何情况下，代理如果想终止合约，都必须以书面&lt;/span&gt;/&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;电邮方式提早于七日内通知&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;平台&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;。代理的表现会&lt;/span&gt;3&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;个月审核一次，如代理已不是现有的合作成员则本合约书可以在任何时间终止。如合作伙伴违反合约条例，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;平台&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;有权立即终止合约。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:28px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;7.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;在没有&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;平台&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;许可下，代理不能透露及授权&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;平台&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;相关密资料，包括代理所获得的回馈、佣金报表、计算等&lt;/span&gt;;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;代理有义务在合约终止后仍执行机密档及资料的保密。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:28px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;8.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;在合约终止后，代理及&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;平台&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;将不须要履行双方的权利及义务。终止合约并不会解除代理于终止合约前应履行的义务。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 37);
